      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那WARMUP和INIT这两个分支怎么区分？看起来都和START信号有关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "START"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关键在MODE参数。如果START时MODE=WARM_UP，走WARMUP路径；普通START直接进INIT。WARMUP完成后自动回到OFF，这是预热自检的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "MODE",
        "WARM_UP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，OFF到WARMUP和INIT的分支我画好了。INIT之后是PRECOOL对吧？触发条件是init_seconds计时完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "PRECOOL",
        "init_seconds"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PRECOOL是预冷阶段。然后判断T5和TSP的关系——当T5降到TSP减去precool_band以下时，进入RUN状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRECOOL",
        "RUN",
