    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，READY是Infra_LoadBalancer的就绪标志。只要ready flag为true，不管当前在哪个阶段都可以转入READY。READY清除后返回RUN。",
      "elements_involved": [
