      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要一个SAFE_SHUTDOWN安全关机状态吧？我注意到INIT、PRECOOL、RUN、READY、HOLD、WARMUP都应该能进入它。",
